Param.Name: TopDownImage
Param.Description: Name of image to use as 1:1 scale top-down view of template

Param.Name: TopDownMinSize
Param.Description: Size in pixels when icon starts to be displayed instead of top-down image

Param.Name: TopDownPxPerMtr
Param.Description: Resolution of top-down image, in pixels per meter. This is only used when topDownSize is 0, otherwise topDownSize takes priority.

Param.Name: TopDownSize
Param.Description: Size of top-down image, in meters
